text: Satpal Jamba or Satpal Kanyan, is an Indian politician from Jamba village in Haryana. He became a member of the Haryana Legislative Assembly in 2024. He represents the Pundri Assembly constituency as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. ==References== Category:Politicians from Haryana Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians
title: Satpal Jamba
